<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idee2c9b27-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9" identifier="/us/usc/t7/s385a"><num value="385a">§ 385a.</num><heading> Authorization of appropriations</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">There is authorized to be appropriated each fiscal year necessary appropriations to enable the Secretary of Agriculture to carry on the cooperative experiments contemplated by <ref href="/us/usc/t7/s385">section 385 of this title</ref>.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idee2c9b28-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9">(<ref href="/us/act/1927-03-03/ch367/s2">Mar. 3, 1927, ch. 367, § 2</ref>, as added <ref href="/us/act/1928-02-04/ch24">Feb. 4, 1928, ch. 24</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/45/57">45 Stat. 57</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
